	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_001936_0001"><!--pb/@n='41r'--></pb>
<lb/><p><space extent="1" unit="chars"/><placeName><geogName type="cataract">Cataracts</geogName></placeName> <date when="1863-07-05">5<hi rend="sup">th</hi> July</date></p>
<lb/><p rend="center"><space extent="1" unit="words"/>1863</p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">My dear <persName>Waller</persName></p>
<lb/><p><space extent="2" unit="chars"/>I am sorry
<lb/>that I can only
<lb/>give you a line
<lb/>for the men are
<lb/>waiting and I wish
<lb/>to tell you more
<lb/>according to your
<lb/>wish - I shall take
<lb/>an early opportunity
<lb/>of writing you</p>
<lb/><p>I cannot but
<lb/>say that <placeName><settlement type="village">Morambala</settlement></placeName>

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_001936_0002"><!--pb/@n='41v'--></pb>
<lb/>seems as <w>healthy<supplied>-</supplied>
<lb/>looking</w> as up here
<lb/>on the hills but
<lb/>I <choice><sic>dont</sic><corr>don't</corr></choice> know. I
<lb/>thought the <term type="occupation">bishop</term>
<lb/>whom we liked
<lb/>very well indeed
<lb/>ought to visit both
<lb/><placeName><settlement type="village">Ukames</settlement></placeName> &amp; <placeName><settlement type="village">Morambala</settlement></placeName>
<lb/>before deciding.</p>
<lb/><p><persName>Clementino</persName> will
<lb/>be glad of bills on
<lb/><placeName><settlement type="city">Bombay</settlement></placeName> for his
<lb/>money from
<lb/><persName>Thorton</persName> - but

	

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_001936_0003"><!--pb/@n='42r'--></pb>
<lb/>I shall revert to the
<lb/>subject. We go up
<lb/>to the <placeName><region>North of the Lake</region></placeName>
<lb/>if we can. My
<lb/>kind salutations
<lb/>to <persName>Procter</persName> &amp; <persName>Rowley</persName>
<lb/>I would have
<lb/>written <persName>Procter</persName> had
<lb/>it been possible
<lb/>but I hope he will
<lb/>take my kind
<lb/>good bye through
<lb/>you &amp; that - the
<lb/>Highest may be
<lb/>his shield and
<lb/>comforter</p>

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_001936_0004"><!--pb/@n='42v'--></pb>
<lb/><p>I am ever yours.</p>
<lb/><p rend="center"><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>

<lb/><cb rend="vertical"/>
<lb/><ab><hi rend="underline" hand="#U"><persName>David <choice><orig>Livingston</orig><reg>Livingstone</reg></choice></persName></hi></ab>
			
